@startuml Sequence_Dashboard
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #EBF5FB
  ParticipantBorderColor #2980B9
  ArrowColor #2C3E50
  LifeLineBorderColor #BDC3C7
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #ECF0F1
  ActorBackgroundColor #FDEBD0
  ActorBorderColor #E67E22
}
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #F9A825

title Sequence Diagram — Dashboard & Notifikasi

actor "Pengguna" as User
participant "React Frontend" as FE
participant "Sanctum Middleware" as Auth
participant "DashboardController" as DC
participant "NotificationController" as NC
database "Database" as DB

autonumber

== Load Dashboard ==

User -> FE : Akses halaman Dashboard\n(setelah login berhasil)

FE -> Auth : GET /api/me\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}
Auth -> DB : SELECT user WITH role
DB --> Auth : User + Role info
Auth --> FE : 200 { user }
FE -> FE : Simpan user context\n(role, nama)

FE -> Auth : GET /api/dashboard
Auth -> Auth : Validasi token (semua role)
Auth -> DC : index(request)

DC -> DB : Query 1:\nSELECT COUNT(*) products WHERE is_active=1
DC -> DB : Query 2:\nSELECT COUNT(*) transactions (hari ini)
DC -> DB : Query 3:\nSELECT SUM(total_amount) transaksi (hari ini)
DC -> DB : Query 4:\nSELECT COUNT(*) low_stock products
DC -> DB : Query 5:\nSELECT COUNT(*) underperforming\n(latest per product)
DC -> DB : Query 6:\nRevenue 7 hari terakhir

DB --> DC : Semua agregasi

DC --> FE : 200 {\n  total_products,\n  today_transactions,\n  today_revenue,\n  low_stock_count,\n  underperforming_count,\n  recent_revenue: [...]\n}

FE -> FE : Render kartu statistik\n& grafik mini

== Load Notifikasi ==

FE -> Auth : GET /api/notifications
Auth -> NC : index(request)
NC -> DB : SELECT * FROM notifications\nORDER BY created_at DESC\nLIMIT 10
DB --> NC : Notifications
NC --> FE : 200 [ { id, type, message,\n  is_read, created_at }, ... ]

FE -> FE : Tampilkan badge\njumlah notifikasi belum dibaca
FE --> User : Dashboard siap dengan\nnotifikasi

== Tandai Notifikasi Dibaca ==

User -> FE : Klik notifikasi
FE -> Auth : POST /api/notifications/{id}/read
Auth -> NC : markAsRead(notification)
NC -> DB : UPDATE notifications\nSET is_read = true\nWHERE id = ?
DB --> NC : Updated
NC --> FE : 200 { message: "Berhasil" }
FE -> FE : Update badge count\nHilangkan highlight notifikasi

User -> FE : Klik "Tandai Semua Dibaca"
FE -> Auth : POST /api/notifications/read-all
Auth -> NC : markAllAsRead(request)
NC -> DB : UPDATE notifications\nSET is_read = true
DB --> NC : Updated all
NC --> FE : 200 { message: "Semua dibaca" }
FE --> User : Badge = 0\nSemua notifikasi hilang highlight

@enduml
